<h3 id="follow-up">Follow up:</h3>
<ul>
  <li>It is very easy to come up with a solution with run time <code class="highlighter-rouge">O(n*sizeof(integer))</code>. But can you do it in linear time <code class="highlighter-rouge">O(n)</code> /possibly in a single pass?</li>
  <li>Space complexity should be <code class="highlighter-rouge">O(n)</code>.</li>
  <li>Can you do it like a boss? Do it without using any builtin function like <code class="highlighter-rouge">__builtin_popcount</code> in c++ or in any other language.</li>
</ul>
